  ID: MenAtArms2
  Name: Giorgio
  Icon: {fileID: -2105629146, guid: d556a7f542c7d03429c5a535ce31a084, type: 3}
  Description: "Wound: Arrow wound festering with infection, arm swollen, black veins
    creeping outward.\n\nStory: Giorgio, a Venetian trader turned soldier, reeks
    of rot as fever consumes him. He confesses between shivers that he left behind
    a caravan bound for Rhodes \u2014 and a wife who believed he would return with
    riches. Instead, he fears she will inherit only debt, disgrace, and the memory
    of a husband who failed her.\n\n\nRequired bandages to heal: 3"
  slotNumber: 1
  requiredResource: Bandage
  requiredAmount: 3
